{
  "stem": "280.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, they had a big iron kettle, which was-- which was built into the ground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stirred.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the they made-- they made jam out of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a huge amount, you know, because-- it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, you know, in the night, sitting around the deck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was already chill-- chilly, the air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was something that I shall always remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was considered a city girl, so it was a big treat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The games, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember we went almost every day to some kind of excursion, to some orchard somewhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took a long picnic-like, and we spent the day there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, what I shall never remember, when the cattle-- the-- the cows came home in the evening-- They were out in the pasture during the day.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they left-- they were picked up early in the morning, at dawn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the early evening, when they came home, there was one man who was watching them and guiding them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But each one turned in-- into their own yard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cows knew where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was just, for me-- I-- I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First I went elementary school, to the Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which, I told you, it was a very nice building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I came to this country and my children went, of course, to Hebrew school here, the building, it was a big disappointment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In America, my children to-- to-- to go to school in such a small-- you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a beautiful, three-story building, built for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was part of a big half of a block where the major-- the major shul was, which was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
